and they said you could go.

08:50.560 --> 08:52.595
Come on,
you're gonna have a great time.

08:52.597 --> 08:57.568
You're gonna make some friends.
You'll make some memories.

09:01.606 --> 09:03.107
Can we just do this?

09:06.077 --> 09:08.277
Do what?

09:08.279 --> 09:10.579
Just drive.

09:10.581 --> 09:11.850
Drive and listen.

09:13.885 --> 09:17.722
Listen to this music.
Me and you.

09:20.156 --> 09:21.990
Just listen to the words.

09:21.992 --> 09:25.927
