10:16.680 --> 10:19.348
Go on. Get outta here.

10:19.350 --> 10:21.820
Bye, Mom.

10:28.358 --> 10:33.128
Oh, gosh. I can do this.
I can do this.

10:33.130 --> 10:36.699
No Walkmans at camp.
They'll take it up.

10:36.701 --> 10:37.936
Are you kidding?

10:39.837 --> 10:44.672
Oh, um, hi.
Uh, I'm... I'm Bart.

10:44.674 --> 10:47.976
My friends, like,
they call me Bart.

10:47.978 --> 10:52.047
I know. I'm Shannon. Duh!

10:52.049 --> 10:54.716
- Ready for camp?
- Mmm.

10:54.718 --> 10:56.719
It's totally safe!

10:56.721 --> 10:59.153
See? Safe.

10:59.155 --> 11:01.724
Well,
except for that one kid.

11:01.726 --> 11:04.029
You coming?

11:16.973 --> 11:19.742
Sorry, sorry.
Squeeze in here. Sorry.

11:19.744 --> 11:21.643
Oh, sorry 'bout that!

11:21.645 --> 11:24.680
- Hey, Bart, this is Kent.
- Nice to meet you, Bart.

11:24.682 --> 11:27.749
Hey, bro. This is the cup game.
I'm not very good at it.

11:27.751 --> 11:29.884
Campers.
Campers, up here!

11:29.886 --> 11:31.320
So I'm Rusty.

11:31.322 --> 11:33.122
For those of you
who don't know me,

11:33.124 --> 11:35.324
I'm the Youth Pastor
at Greenville Baptist.

11:35.326 --> 11:36.992
So if you didn't bring
your journals, come up here.

11:36.994 --> 11:38.860
We got one for you.

11:38.862 --> 11:40.863
You're gonna need it
for your session tonight.

11:40.865 --> 11:43.101
- Let's have a great week.
- Bro, sit down. I got you.

11:46.871 --> 11:49.805
So is that like a diary, or?

11:49.807 --> 11:52.774
Kinda, but there's more to it.
Helps get my thoughts ordered.

11:52.776 --> 11:56.277
Prayers, problems, dreams,
stuff I imagine sometimes.

11:56.279 --> 11:57.779
Uh, can I see?

11:57.781 --> 12:00.682
I'm sorry,
I... I didn't know.

12:00.684 --> 12:03.451
B-9, you're with me for
kitchen duty, let's do it.

12:03.453 --> 12:05.921
Well, that's me.
See you later, okay?

12:05.923 --> 12:07.790
Hey, Bart,
I got your journal.

12:07.792 --> 12:09.090
Ooh! Kent!

12:17.802 --> 12:20.069
Here. Here you go.
I'm sorry.

12:30.180 --> 12:33.382
That's mint.
I didn't know you could draw.

12:33.384 --> 12:35.850
