like that?

12:35.852 --> 12:38.821
Come with me
if you want to live!

12:38.823 --> 12:41.156
We're sneaking out.

12:41.158 --> 12:45.827
So what do you wanna be
when you grow up, an artist?

12:45.829 --> 12:50.132
Eh, or a football player.
That's what my dad was.

12:50.134 --> 12:53.335
He was really good, actually.
Kind of famous in college.

12:53.337 --> 12:56.504
We're gonna get
in so much trouble for this.

12:56.506 --> 12:58.473
I know, right?
Got some great stuff.

12:58.475 --> 13:01.343
Like industrial grade.
Set it all up this afternoon.

13:01.345 --> 13:03.845
So you guys are gonna go
over there

13:03.847 --> 13:05.750
and face in the north direction,
got it?

13:08.419 --> 13:11.255
And also,
did you know Bart can draw?

13:13.189 --> 13:14.425
Hi.

13:17.794 --> 13:21.162
- So you can draw?
- I guess so, a little bit.

13:21.164 --> 13:24.867
Bart, I'm terrified you saw
what was written in my journal.

13:24.869 --> 13:26.869
- Did you?
- No.

13:26.871 --> 13:29.003
- Wh-what're you talking about?
- You're lying.

13:29.005 --> 13:30.873
You saw every word,
didn't you?

13:30.875 --> 13:34.243
Maybe.

13:34.245 --> 13:37.546
Well, then here goes.
You know what I think?

13:37.548 --> 13:39.848
I think that someday
we're gonna fall in love,

13:39.850 --> 13:43.118
get married,
and that's our destiny.

13:43.120 --> 13:44.987
And now I'm mortified.

13:44.989 --> 13:46.455
I'm gonna walk down this hill
and help Kent.

13:46.457 --> 13:49.090
Wa-wa-wa-wait wait.
Shannon, please stay.

13:49.092 --> 13:53.128
Why? Afraid of the dark?
Afraid of monsters?

13:53.130 --> 13:55.799
I just don't like
being alone.

14:29.400 --> 14:31.365
All right, come on, kids.

14:31.367 --> 14:33.003
Bart, Bart!

14:34.505 --> 14:37.505
- Here. It's my favorite.
- Sweet.

14:37.507 --> 14:39.941
And I wanna be a singer
just like her someday.

14:39.943 --> 14:41.609
Thank you so much.

14:41.611 --> 14:45.150
My parents are here pick me up.
Bye!

15:02.900 --> 15:06.634
Last stop. This is you.

15:06.636 --> 15:10.071
It was good to meet you, Bart.
I'm gonna see you on Sunday?

15:10.073 --> 15:11.442
Yeah. Yeah.

15:24.486 --> 15:25.556
Hey.

15:32.630 --> 15:36.998
Momma? Momma...

15:37.000 --> 15:38.133
Where's Momma?

15:38.135 --> 15:41.235
She's gone.

15:41.237 --> 15:43.138
Gone where?

15:43.140 --> 15:46.407
She ran off.
She ain't coming back.

15:46.409 --> 15:48.379
Just you and me now.

15:53.350 --> 15:55.417
When will she be back?

15:55.419 --> 15:57.484
