and she don't want you neither.

16:01.991 --> 16:05.192
What did you do?

16:05.194 --> 16:07.528
Are you bowing up on me, boy?

16:07.530 --> 16:10.532
You hurt her, didn't you?!

16:10.534 --> 16:13.134
- Hey!
- You hurt her like you hurt me!

16:13.136 --> 16:14.302
Hey!

16:14.304 --> 16:17.038
Nothing! That's what I did!

16:17.040 --> 16:18.242
Nothing!

16:26.116 --> 16:28.218
She didn't leave 'cause of me.

16:51.475 --> 16:54.075
I'm sorry, Mom!

16:54.077 --> 16:55.579
What did I do?!

16:57.981 --> 17:01.082
Take me, Mom, please!

17:01.084 --> 17:02.452
Stop!

17:16.666 --> 17:19.002
So did you ever
see her again?

17:20.371 --> 17:22.404
Uh,
she'd call now and then.

17:22.406 --> 17:25.240
I tried to live with her once,
one summer in junior high,

17:25.242 --> 17:28.275
but she was in another bad
relationship.

17:28.277 --> 17:30.311
Worse, actually.

17:30.313 --> 17:35.117
Um, my dad drove up and threw
the guy off a staircase

17:35.119 --> 17:37.119
onto the hood of his car
and threatened to kill him

17:37.121 --> 17:38.753
if he ever hurt her again

17:38.755 --> 17:42.124
and then grabbed me
and took me home.

17:42.126 --> 17:44.492
It's kind of ironic.

17:44.494 --> 17:48.463
Um, that was about it.

17:48.465 --> 17:50.234
So what did you do?

17:52.402 --> 17:56.106
I tried to get good at the only
thing my dad really cared about.

18:01.078 --> 18:03.145
- Hey, there.
- Hey there, darlin'.

18:03.147 --> 18:05.147
That's so corny.

18:05.149 --> 18:06.680
