- Shut up!

18:13.724 --> 18:15.223
I like it.

18:15.225 --> 18:19.226
Millard!
Get over here, now.

18:19.228 --> 18:21.565
I love you.

18:23.667 --> 18:24.769
I know.

18:26.269 --> 18:28.235
Unbelievable.

18:28.237 --> 18:30.374
- Break!
- Break!

18:59.736 --> 19:03.341
Hey. Just give me a second.

19:06.677 --> 19:09.211
- It's sour.
- Jeez.

19:09.213 --> 19:11.249
It's a month past its date.

19:14.217 --> 19:15.485
I'll make Pop-Tarts, then.

19:17.454 --> 19:19.687
Just a few things I ask you
to do around here, Bart,

19:19.689 --> 19:21.322
a few things.

19:23.560 --> 19:27.228
I caught before I ran, Dad,
at practice today.

19:27.230 --> 19:29.330
Almost scored.

19:29.332 --> 19:32.199
- How many of them did it take?
- What?

19:32.201 --> 19:34.235
To get you down on the ground.
How many'd it take?

19:34.237 --> 19:38.473
- Just one. It's just practice.
- One?

19:38.475 --> 19:40.675
Nobody could never
bring <i>me</i> down.

19:40.677 --> 19:45.280
Took the whole football team.
It's the way I live my life.

19:45.282 --> 19:48.250
Life hits me,
I hit back harder.

19:48.252 --> 19:52.123
I don't go down.
Not then, not now, not never.

19:53.923 --> 19:55.659
You understand?

20:00.397 --> 20:01.732
Break!

20:04.267 --> 20:06.201
<i>I don't go down.</i>

20:06.203 --> 20:08.270
<i>You go down too easy.
That's your problem.</i>

20:59.422 --> 21:01.322
What'd they say?

21:01.324 --> 21:03.824
They said you can't play.

21:03.826 --> 21:05.459
For how long?

21:05.461 --> 21:06.863
Ever.

21:12.902 --> 21:15.337
Well, that's disappointing.

21:15.339 --> 21:17.542
Yeah. Yeah, it is.

21:26.350 --> 21:28.817
- Whoa! Hey.
- Sorry.

21:28.819 --> 21:31.453
