is not stupid.

21:35.025 --> 21:37.491
You just have to pick a new
elective to replace football.

21:37.493 --> 21:39.461
- Yeah.
- Okay.

21:39.463 --> 21:43.264
Oh, man, ever have aspirations
of being a seamstress?

21:43.266 --> 21:46.834
Well, that's full, so.
They're, like, all full.

21:46.836 --> 21:49.571
- Yeah.
- Except this one.

21:49.573 --> 21:53.308
- What?
- Glee Club.

